width: 960px; display: block\">\r\n<h2 style=\"background-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 28px; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; height: auto; color: rgb(53,53,53); font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; padding-top: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">华硕5重防护</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"background-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1; margin: 0px 0px 0.4em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; height: auto; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; padding-top: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">全方位保护主板,主机更安全,使用更可靠</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em\">华硕主板藉由独家5重防护来保护您的电脑：DIGI+ VRM数字供电控制提供精准的CPU供电控制；ESD静电防护，延长料件使用寿命，让华硕主板远离静电干扰和损害；板载可复式保险丝（自恢复保险丝）防止内存因过电流和短路损坏；防潮不锈钢I/O 接口，保护接口不受腐蚀侵害。华硕提供的这一系列的防护技术为主机提供了超强的安全可靠性和延长了耐用度。</p>\r\n<img class=\"center\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; display: block; max-width: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: auto; margin-left: auto; vertical-align: middle; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: auto\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/CN/products/Y4c8h5gYt9uQazAG/5X.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<section style=\"position: relative; display: block; float: left\"></section>\r\n<div class=\"unit_cut\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 960px; display: block\">\r\n<h2 style=\"background-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 28px; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; height: auto; color: rgb(53,53,53); font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; padding-top: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">DIGI+ VRM数字供电控制</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"background-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1; margin: 0px 0px 0.4em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; height: auto; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; padding-top: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">精准的数字供电控制,系统长效稳定</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em\">VRM (电压调校模块)是主板设计中最重要的部件之一。良好的 VRM可智能的根据 CPU 实际所需功耗来提供精确的供电。华硕领先的数字供电设计采用超快的感应和响应速度，高效地提供精准的CPU供电。精确的供电更可减少功耗浪费，保障供电持续，让系统获得更高的效率转换率与增强稳定性。</p>\r\n<img class=\"center\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; display: block; max-width: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: auto; margin-left: auto; vertical-align: middle; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: auto\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/UjihzQKhBmQmiVsY/digi.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<section style=\"position: relative; display: block; float: left\"></section>\r\n<div class=\"unit_cut\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 960px; display: block\">\r\n<h2 style=\"background-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 28px; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; height: auto; color: rgb(53,53,53); font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; padding-top: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">内存过流保护</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"background-image: none; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1; margin: 0px 0px 0.4em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \'Arial Unicode MS\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; height: auto; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; padding-top: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">预防短路造成的主板和内存损毁</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4em\">板载可复式保险丝可有效防止过载或短路情况,在I/O端口到DRAM之间增强电子线路保护,保障系统和设备的安全使用，延长设备寿命。</p>\r\n<img class=\"center\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; display: block; max-width: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: auto; margin-left: auto; vertical-align: middle; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: auto\" src=\"ht