 colspan=\"2\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">891<font face=\"宋体\">及</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">893</font><font face=\"宋体\">中的液晶屏幕分辨率实际上为</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">320(</font><font face=\"宋体\">宽）</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">*240</font><font face=\"宋体\">（高），所谓</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">960</font><font face=\"宋体\">意思就是红绿蓝&nbsp;</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">3</font><font face=\"宋体\">色各</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">320</font><font face=\"宋体\">加起来等于</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">960</font><font face=\"宋体\">意思（</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">320</font><font face=\"宋体\">&times;</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">3</font><font face=\"宋体\">），实际上点分辨率就是</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">320*240</font></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; width: 142.05pt; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">新工程宝采用液晶屏幕点分辨率为<font face=\"Times New Roman\">480*320</font><font face=\"宋体\">如按照上述算法就是</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1440(480</font><font face=\"宋体\">&times;</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">3)*320</font></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 80.1pt;\">\r\n            <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 142pt; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px;\" class=\"p0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; width: 142.05pt; border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px;\" class=\"p0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"189\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-width: 0.5pt 0.5pt 0.5pt medium; border-style: solid solid solid none; width: 142.05pt; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">数码放大有&nbsp;<font face=\"Times New Roman\">4</font><font face=\"宋体\">挡&nbsp;</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><font face=\"宋体\">、（适应屏幕）&nbsp;</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2</font><font face=\"宋体\">、（</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1X</font><font face=\"宋体\">）&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">3</font><font face=\"宋体\">、（</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2X&nbsp;</font><font face=\"宋体\">）&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">4</font><font face=\"宋体\">、（</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">4X</font><font face=\"宋体\">）&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n            <p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px;\" class=\"p0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.33333396911621px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"p0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.33333396911621px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt;\">2、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold;\" class=\"15\">数码放大功能</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.33333396911621px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"p0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.33333396911621px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"p0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.33333396911621px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">1<font face=\"宋体\">、由于工程宝是手持设备，受便携性限制，太大液晶屏幕将无法很难移动施工。但</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">3.5</font><font face=\"宋体\">寸小屏幕和普通监视器相比较显示内容画面太小，即使分辩率足够，眼睛也很难分析到细节内容，所以数码放大功能就将屏幕变成大尺寸监视器一样大小，将显示内容局部显示出来，方便对画面细节分析。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.33333396911621px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">2.<font face=\"宋体\">、通过数码放大功能，可以将高分辩率内容按</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><font face=\"宋体\">：</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><font face=\"宋体\">（</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><font face=\"宋体\">：</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2&nbsp;</font><font face=\"宋体\">，</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><font face=\"宋体\">：</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">4</font><font face=\"宋体\">）比例局部显示出来，如图，</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">PAL&nbsp;</font><font face=\"宋体\">制式分辨率&nbsp;为</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">720</font><font face=\"宋体\">&times;</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">576</font><font face=\"宋体\">，&nbsp;目前液晶显示屏分辨率是</font></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;480<font face=\"宋体\">&times;</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">320&nbsp;</font><font face=\"宋体\">。无法按</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><font face=\"宋体\">：</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1&nbsp;</font><font face=\"宋体\">点数进行显示，只能缩小后再显示出来。通过数码放大功能，可以按</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><font face=\"宋体\">：</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><font face=\"宋体\">点数甚至</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><font face=\"宋体\">：</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2&nbsp;&nbsp;1</font><font face=\"宋体\">：</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">4</font><font face=\"宋体\">比率显示局部&nbsp;画面，</font></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">然后通过方向键进行显示中局部内容移动显示，可以突破显示屏分辨率限制，对图像画面进行非常细致分析。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.33333396911621px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"p0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.33333396911621px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">在实际中，摄像机中常见的边角对焦模糊，镜头上是否有灰尘异物，还有安装监控摄像头过程中对细节位置能否显示清晰等情况，在低分辨率小尺寸屏幕很难观察到的细节情况，有了数码放大功能，在工程施工和设备维护时将提供更细致的调试显示效果。</span></p>\r\n<p>外形尺寸</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">170mm&nbsp;x&nbsp;99mm&nbsp;x&nbsp;48mm</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;/&nbsp;293g</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','images/201310/thumb_img/5402_thumb_G_1382760818103.jpg','images/201310/goods_img/5402_G_1382760818879.jpg','images/201310/source_img/5402_G_1382760818450.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1382760818','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1382761234','0','','0','0','0','0');
