3.5</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold;\">英寸高清大屏幕，中文全功能版</span></p>\r\n            </span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <td width=\"553\" valign=\"top\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0pt; width: 415.3pt;\">\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\"><br />\r\n            </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;工程宝</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 9pt;\">DT-N94</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">，是为视频监控工程现场安装、维护所使用的专业测试工具。具有视频显示、PTZ控制、DC12V电源输出、测试、条发生器、RS485数据捕捉、网线测试、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">数码变倍，截图及录像、带高精度万用表</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">等功能。</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; font-weight: bold;\">产品突出功能：</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">1、屏幕高清：屏幕分辨率高，支持高线数摄像头&nbsp;：3.5英寸&nbsp;高清晰LCD显示屏，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">480*RGB*320（HVGA）分辨率，64K色；</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">2、数码放大功能：视频输入图像可以局部放大，看清图像细节；</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">3、截图和录像功能：支持视频输入截图及录像；</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">4、高精度万用表：内置高精度全功能数字万用表功能，3.5英寸大屏幕高清晰显示，读</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">数清晰，3&nbsp;3/4位(6600计数)专业数字万用表，可用于测量直流电压、交流电压、直流电流、交流电流、电阻测量、通断测试、二极管测量、电容测量，自动/手动量程转换，差值测量及锁定，功能齐全，测量准确度高，使用方便。</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">其他功能：</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 14.9pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">1、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">3.5英寸&nbsp;大屏幕高清显示，显示摄像机图像</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 36.75pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">DT-N9</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">视频测试仪，&nbsp;采用了3.5英寸大屏幕高清数字</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 10.5pt;\">LCD</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">监视器，&nbsp;显示区域更广更清晰，更加直观方便地显示出摄像机图像效果。</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 36.75pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">LCD监视器亮度、对比度、色彩饱和度可调，&nbsp;背光亮度可调适合野外施工和维护。</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 17.95pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;2、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">视频信号强度测量</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 36.75pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">DT-N9</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">视频测试仪，新增了视频信号强度测量，测试视频信号是否衰减或过高。视频信号由于视频线缆过长会造成信号衰减，视频信号的衰减会造成图像暗淡，降低图像动态范围；如视频信号过强，会造成虚影，降低图像的清晰度。DT-N9</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">的视频信号测量功能，实时显示视频信号的电平值，如果超出范围，仪器的屏幕会有提示信息显示。</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 17.95pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">3</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">多制式图像发生器发送彩色条，检测传输通道</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 36.75pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">DT-N9</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">可通过视频</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 10.5pt;\">OUT</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">端口，发送多种制式（PAL，NTSC）彩色图型条，图型条有：白、黄、青、绿、粉、红、蓝、黑共八种颜色，通过&nbsp;中心的监视器是否接收到彩色图型条来判断视频通道是否正常传输，同时，通过&nbsp;中心接收到的彩色图型条，可以判断是否因为传输有衰减或干扰造成颜色偏差。该设备也可由视频</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 10.5pt;\">OUT</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">端口发送彩色图案，同时在</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 10.5pt;\">IN</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">端口接收并显示，适合视频传输的现场检测，如视频光端机、视频线缆等。</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 17.95pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">12V电源输出，为摄像机供电</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 37.05pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">DT-N9</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">视频测试仪专门为摄像机的供电而设计了12V&nbsp;1A的电源输出端口，为摄像机提供临时的供电。主要应用于一些摄像机的现场演示和测试，同时，对于一些需要安装摄像机的场地，因为项目实施之前现场没有电源，必须找到临时的电源为摄像机供电，DT-N9</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">的供电输出就发挥了必要的作用。</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 17.95pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">5</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">音频测试功能，测试前端音频设备的声音是否正常</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 37.8pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">DT-N9</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt;\">视频测试仪的音频测试功能，可以对视频前端的拾音器等音频设备进行测试。</span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin: 5pt 0px 5pt 17.95pt; padding: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">6</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold;\">、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; paddi